title: FL Studio 11.0.4 incl. x64 Beta 6 & March Update
description:
NOTE: You must be running 64 Bit windows to use 64 Bit FL Studio

How to install: The 64 Bit beta installation files are added to the FL Studio 11.0.4 installation folder as follows ...

Install and register FL Studio 11.0.4 using key.

Install FL Studio 64 Bit 
The installtion will add itself to the folder ..:Program Files (x86)Image-LineFL Studio 11 as FL64.exe. Use this to start FL Studio 64 Bit.

Install the March update for FL Studio 64 Bit -


NOTE :
If you are not able to keep your cool, even knowing this is a beta, when things go wrong then DO NOT USE THIS VERSION. 


Known Problems

CPU Memory panel - Memory display incorrect
Denoiser tool in Edison not implemented
Scripts in Edison and Slicex not stable (improved)
ZGameEditor Visualizer: video clip as texture isn't implemented
In some cases, changing the ASIO driver can crash. Please let us know when it does.
DirectWave's file import is experimental, it may or may not work at this time. Please let us know when it doesn't.
It's possible that the 64bit ogg vorbis codec interferes with tv tuners. Let us know when this happens

Enjoy.
